CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 21, 1959, pg. B2, reads: "GIRL SCOUT COOKS - These young ladies, shown with their troop leader, are Girl Scouts from Troop 1303, and they are engaged in earning a cooking badge... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Girl Scouts from troops 1303 and 104, including one standing in front of oven with cookies, earning cooking badge in Equitable Gas demonstration kitchen
